author: felicity
msg: update sa-learn docs.  rename (but keep backwards compat support for) --rebuild and --no-rebuild to be the more accurate --sync and --nosync since the option specifies that a journal sync should/should not occur... there's really no rebuilding involved.

author: felicity
msg: bug 3164: 2.6x allowed old databaes to be used for check(), dump(), etc (anything that didn't write to the db).  for 3.0 we're dropping that support -- databases must now be upgraded before they're usable.
